fe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182827\/low-cost-interior-designers-india-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A beautiful modern bathroom with textured tiles and a white granite countertop with specs of blue<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A 3 BHK Flat Interior Design Cost<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you own an apartment and are looking to do up the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/3bhk-interior-design\/\"><strong>interiors of a 3BHK flat<\/strong><\/a> the cost varies depending on the square feet. This can range anywhere between <strong>7 Lakh to 12 Lakh<\/strong> and if it&#8217;s of premium quality. And you&#8217;re looking to deck up the place it could cost up to 15 Lakh depending on the quality of laminate, designs, finishes and also paint&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182808\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost.jpg\" alt=\"Living room with stone cladding, false ceiling and chandelier in 3 bhk interior design cost varies.\" class=\"wp-image-16959\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182808\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182808\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182808\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182808\/3-bhk-interior-design-cost-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A gorgeous living room with stone cladding, a false wall with a wooden plank and a white chandelier<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Cost For Interior Design Of A 2 BHK<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If it\u2019s a 2BHK flat the cost for interior design will range approximately between <strong>3.5 Lakh to 7 Lakh<\/strong> for basic quality. And a premium home can cost upto anything between 7 Lakh to 10 Lakh. Again it all depends on the square feet, finishes and materials you want to use. The price of interiors will increase based on style and structure too.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182802\/2bhk-interior-design-cost.jpg\" alt=\"2BHK interior design cost of the dining room with a six-seater dining table and box cabinets\" class=\"wp-image-16958\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182802\/2bhk-interior-design-cost.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182802\/2bhk-interior-design-cost-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182802\/2bhk-interior-design-cost-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182802\/2bhk-interior-design-cost-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A smart dining area with box cabinets made from transparent glass and a six-seater dining table<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p> Also, Read About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/2bhk-interior-design\/\">2BHK Interior Design<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">The Cost For Interior Design Of A 1 BHK Flat<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A 1 BHK flat\u2019s interior design cost for basic normal to medium finishes ranges anything between <strong>2 Lakh to 3.5 Lakh<\/strong> with a basic finish. If you want interiors with a premium finish, it can go up to as much as 5 Lakhs.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182756\/1-bhk-flat-interior-design-cost.jpg\" alt=\"1 bhk flat interior design cost of the master bedroom with a textured wall and dressing table\" class=\"wp-image-16957\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182756\/1-bhk-flat-interior-design-cost.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182756\/1-bhk-flat-interior-design-cost-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182756\/1-bhk-flat-interior-design-cost-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182756\/1-bhk-flat-interior-design-cost-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A master bedroom with textured wallpaper, queen sized bed and a long length mirror with a pouffe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read About <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/1bhk-interior-design\/\">1BHK House Designs<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Secrets To Hiring Interior Designer For Less in 2024?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/u0ifOI5AwQA?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cost For Interiors Of A Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The living room is the most wanted and most well-spent area in your home. So if you want to sit back and relax with comfort and style it&#8217;s super important to know about how much <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">living room interior design<\/a> will cost. You will need to budget <strong>INR 20,000 &#8211; 50,000<\/strong> approximately for a living room with basic interiors and furniture. And for a premium one it can range between INR 75,000 &#8211; 1,00,000 Lakh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182820\/living-room-interior-design-cost.jpg\" alt=\"Low cost interior design of the living room with a TV unit with ample storage is the best interior design low cost.\" class=\"wp-image-16961\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182820\/living-room-interior-design-cost.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182820\/living-room-interior-design-cost-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182820\/living-room-interior-design-cost-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/09182820\/living-room-interior-design-cost-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">An elegant hall with a swirling staircase and a TV unit in wood with ample storage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This is about how much we at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> charge for interior designs. Let us know what you think! Send us an email. Can&#8217;t wait to hear from you!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/first-timers-guide-to-working-with-interior-designer\/\">How To Working With An Interior Designer<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/10-questions-to-ask-an-interior-designer\/\">10 Question To Ask An Interior Designer<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/cities\/interior-designers-bangalore\/\">Home Interior Designers In Bengaluru<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Interior Designer Cost<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do I compare the cost of different interio<\/strong>r <strong>designers?<\/strong><br>Before comparing the cost of different interior designers, you need to define your requirements and have a clear understanding of your budget and personal style. Next, look for interior designers who have experience in your style preference and fit your budget. Get a final quote and compare the services included in each designer&#8217;s package. Thoroughly verify what is included in the pricing and check for any additional costs not included in the quote.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How can I get the most value for my money when hiring an interior designer?<\/strong><br>It is important to be clear about what services you are looking for before hiring an interior designer. Define your budget and timelines and clearly communicate them to the interior designer. Collect images of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">home interior designs<\/a> you like to give the designer a fair understanding of your style and preferences. Make sure the designs created by the interior designer are not just aesthetic but also functional. This will help you get the most value for your money when hiring an interior designer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Are there any hidden costs associated with hiring an interior designer?<\/strong><br>When you work with reputed brands like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a>, you can rest assured that there are not going to be any hidden costs. Our experienced interior designers share a detailed quote after understanding your requirements and creating realistic 3D renders for your project. There are no hidden costs in our final quote.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are the different pricing models used by interior designers?<\/strong><br>The most common pricing model used by interior designers is the flat fee model where a fixed fee is determined after the final consultation and agreement on the scope of work. In the hourly rate pricing model, the interior designer charges an hourly rate for their services for however long the project lasts. Cost-plus markup, percentage-based, and value-based are some other pricing models used by interior designers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Is it worth hiring an interior designer if I have a tight budget?<\/strong><br>Absolutely! Even if you have a tight budget, hiring an interior designer is worth it as they help you avoid costly mistakes. They come with a lot of experience and industry contacts to get your home interiors done with high-quality materials and within the specified budget and timelines. This saves you valuable time and effort and you get a home that you will love living in.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/